## Feature Implementation Requirements

This table shows which features require implementation and which are auto-handled by the framework:

| Feature | Implementation Required? | Notes |
|---------|-------------------------|-------|
| **Tools** | ‚úÖ Always | Every tool must have an implementation method |
| **Prompts** | ‚úÖ Always | All prompts require implementation as methods |
| **Static Resources** | ‚ùå No | Framework serves literal data directly |
| **Dynamic Resources** | ‚úÖ Required | Must implement when `returns` field is used |

### Quick Reference

**You MUST implement:**
- ‚úÖ All tools (every tool needs a method)
- ‚úÖ All prompts (every prompt needs a method)
- ‚úÖ Dynamic resources (when `returns` field contains type definitions)

**Framework handles automatically:**
- ‚úÖ Static resources (when `value` field contains literal values)

### Implementation Checklist

For each feature you define:

1. **Is it a tool?**
   - ‚Üí ‚úÖ **IMPLEMENT** as method (always required)

2. **Is it a prompt?**
   - ‚Üí ‚úÖ **IMPLEMENT** as method (always required)

3. **Is it a resource?**
   - Has `value` field with literals (like `version: '1.0.0'`)? ‚Üí ‚ùå **NO IMPLEMENTATION** needed
   - Has `returns` field with type annotations (like `count: number`)? ‚Üí ‚úÖ **IMPLEMENT** as property

### Examples

**Tool (always needs implementation):**
```typescript
interface MyServer extends IServer {
  name: 'my-server';
  description: 'Example server';
}

interface NameParam extends IParam {
  type: 'string';
  description: 'Person name';
}

interface GreetTool extends ITool {
  name: 'greet';
  params: { name: NameParam };
  result: string;
}

// Must implement
export default class Server implements MyServer {
  greet: GreetTool = async (params) => `Hello, ${params.name}!`;
}
```

**Prompt (implementation required):**
```typescript
interface SummarizePrompt extends IPrompt<{ text: string }> {
  name: 'summarize';
  description: 'Summarize text';
  arguments: {
    text: { description: 'Text to summarize', required: true }
  };
}

// Implementation
summarize: SummarizePrompt = (args) =>
  `Summarize this text: ${args.text}`;
```

**Dynamic Resource (needs implementation):**
```typescript
interface MyServer extends IServer {
  name: 'my-server';
  description: 'Example server';
}

interface StatsResource extends IResource {
  uri: 'stats://requests';
  data: { count: number }; // Type annotation - needs implementation
}

// Must implement
export default class Server implements MyServer {
  'stats://requests': StatsResource = async () => ({ count: 42 });
}
```

